column5: Where is the report?We need pics.I heard that even us Americans may be able to go to Cuba soon. Welcome back Joe

HEY!!!! Virginia twins! How the heck are ya? I got advance copies of the Cuban trip pics but I'm sure he'll post some up for you guys. Just give him a little time to photoshop some clothes on the pics. Shouldn't be too long.
I only care if he covers half the pics bud...
Take all the time you need. I DON'T want to see a bare bear on the beach.   Art
HEY!!!! Virginia twins! How the heck are ya?    Isn't one plumma is just like anuda?
Last I heard we was all right.How have you been? Joe
First thing in the morning.....   its coming!!
